{"id": 2468, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都在哪些事上吃过“来都来了”的亏？", "description": "明知道沉没成本产生了，咋还是难以及时止损？（题图来自：iStock © cako74）", "record_count": 3672, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180716143014W3fwvoNyh2tHAuXV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-18T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 293122, "content": "等公共厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404223}, {"id": 293123, "content": "这个话题，进都进来了，硬着头皮写个回答。", "image": null, "praise_count": 212, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405461}, {"id": 293124, "content": "看人海", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372312}, {"id": 293125, "content": "大老远去香港玩一趟，来都来了，总得买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891733}, {"id": 293131, "content": "出远门找工作 找不到合适的也不能回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071612}, {"id": 295179, "content": "第一次被别人骗在自己脸上用了价格不菲的护肤品", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416522}, {"id": 293132, "content": "高中读理科，大学读工科难道不是极其常见的现象，这也能成为热评？高中不就是文理、艺术生（美术、音乐、表演）、体育生？难道你的高中有工程教育？难道你不知道工科是大学学生比例最大的，本硕博人数均超过30%？", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 293133, "content": "没吃过这种亏", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627183}, {"id": 293901, "content": "读高中", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410254}, {"id": 293134, "content": "生而为人", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362685}, {"id": 293902, "content": "逛街的时候 本来不打算买 但是发现服务态度不错  或者这东西才几块钱或者几十块钱的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20180722200058L3jOoXZyFmPGkcQN", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410267}, {"id": 293136, "content": "干一行恨一行", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 307623}, {"id": 293648, "content": "相亲……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407932}, {"id": 293393, "content": "继续活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407080}, {"id": 293905, "content": "找工作被骗了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1402207}, {"id": 293138, "content": "找了个看起来差不多的人谈对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369436}, {"id": 293394, "content": "前段时间去重庆旅游时晚上排队了两个多小时的队坐了花了20块不到3分钟长江索道", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407093}, {"id": 293139, "content": "不敢分手，还骗着自己说ta可能还爱我", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260391}, {"id": 293140, "content": "爱上一个不该爱的人，还一直爱下去，可能是最大投入的沉没成本了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260391}, {"id": 293396, "content": "上三流大学", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073583}, {"id": 292885, "content": "看了一小半的小说和剧集，会觉得虽然不好看，但很好奇它之后的情节走向", "image": null, "praise_count": 327, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293141, "content": "流着泪也要吃完系列", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425162}, {"id": 293397, "content": "双十一和618本来没啥想买的，但是因为打折还是买了很多没有必要的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590755}, {"id": 292886, "content": "旅行策划了一半，觉得这个地方可能不太好玩，但已经没时间心情再选一个新地方了", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293142, "content": "和女生搞暧昧", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405472}, {"id": 292887, "content": "刚过试用期的工作觉得不适合自己，怕被质疑“频繁跳槽这人是不是有问题”硬着头皮凑满一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 497, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293143, "content": "哪个offer先来就去哪个", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529596}, {"id": 293399, "content": "这高中来都来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407113}, {"id": 293655, "content": "快30了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406606}, {"id": 293144, "content": "到了洗浴，发现和想象中的不一样，只好...大爷搓澡轻点", "image": "img/option/option/20180718134209HPrzO7Wa8mLb3U6x.jpg", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763873}, {"id": 293400, "content": "吃到难吃的要死的垃圾食品 觉得浪费 撑死也要吃完", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407117}, {"id": 293145, "content": "没坐过船?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405524}, {"id": 293146, "content": "去连云港读大学", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405527}, {"id": 294938, "content": "好吧，我是曾经体检当兵，最初只是因为免费体检?结果还真的到部队了，现在都快要回去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415547}, {"id": 293147, "content": "中国大众止损思维欠佳，对边际成本过于看重", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041215}, {"id": 293403, "content": "高中学文，大学习工，心中学史！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407134}, {"id": 293148, "content": "昨天去办健身卡，来都来了，那就办个三年的吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136878}, {"id": 293149, "content": "是指出生在中国这件事儿吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405551}, {"id": 293150, "content": "知道选择错了 也想走到底", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405555}, {"id": 293406, "content": "同学请的电影，还巨差……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407157}, {"id": 293918, "content": "高中是理科，大学学文科（想疯）\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410440}, {"id": 293153, "content": "看种草文，然后点开了京东 天猫  考拉 亚马逊", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405567}, {"id": 293409, "content": "这些现象我居然都没有…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917730}, {"id": 293921, "content": "上大学", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342129}, {"id": 293154, "content": "我觉得做一件事就应该有收获，不管是开心，失落，眼泪还是任何的东西，当然有清晰的目标的人除外", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360661}, {"id": 293155, "content": "冲动消费", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405571}, {"id": 293157, "content": "生而为人啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399255}, {"id": 293414, "content": "等公交迟迟不来，硬等。其实走也走到了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407188}, {"id": 293926, "content": "在游戏里走迷宫遇到不对劲的路，还是要走下去", "image": "img/option/option/20180723025322cTOBXPZCE5WRjoz6", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 54229}, {"id": 293160, "content": "我希望把这种精神应用到Kindle上", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292442}]}